TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi sealed HttpResponseHeader extends System.Enum

summary.span: 可在服务器响应中指定的 HTTP 标头。

span.span: The HTTP headers that can be specified in a server response.

remarks.format: ## Remarks HTTP/1.1 规范中详细介绍了各种标头的相应内容。The appropriate contents of various headers are described in detail in the HTTP/1.1 specification.
